# This directory holds host-specific runtime artifacts:
#   - ib_node, ib_node.pub, ib_node.pem, ib_node.crt  (JWT RS256 keypair)
#   - authorized_keys, config, known_hosts            (SSH metadata)
#
# Everything in this directory is gitignored except this placeholder.
